{"title":"Cotic FlareMAX New Colors for 2024","link":"https://theradavist.com/cotic-flaremax-new-colors-for-2024/","date":1715956588000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/CoticFlareMAX_Colors.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/CoticFlareMAX_Colors.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/CoticFlareMAX_Colors.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/CoticFlareMAX_Colors.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/CoticFlareMAX_Colors.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>We’re not a fan of model years–especially when the updates are tiny geometry tweaks–but it’s nice to have a few new colors offered up each year by small brands. <a href=\"https://www.cotic.co.uk/product/flareMAX\" target=\"_blank\">Cotic’s FlareMAX</a> wowed <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cotic-flaremax-gen5-review/\" target=\"_blank\">John in his review and this week</a>, the UK-made operation announced two new colors of this “Less is More” shred sled: Amethyst and Moonstone.<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/dscf2064_53725381334_o.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/dscf2064_53725381334_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/dscf2064_53725381334_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/dscf2064_53725381334_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/dscf2064_53725381334_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/dscf2021_53725037926_o